Can launch gossip and blabber both names Gossip with two different usernames

can put generic gossip on @connectionsbot. can switch between blabber and generic gossip, same experience for end user, unknown which will have better quality responses. The idea is a generic whats going on, tell me something prompt. followed directly by referecing a matching contribtution. Either by creating a post or by finding best user summary.


User summary matching vs post matching:
- user summary means we can find highly relevant people to talk from the details that have been shared over the course of the conversation
- user summary is simpler creating and updating posts
- post matching removes logic burden from the chatbot which is the most difficult part
- post matching can allow finetuned give to get, making sure people cant just search


benefits of gossip
- guides user to something specific, actionable, and matchable with few network users

benefits of blabber
- least friction, fastest possbile demo

postfinder pros
- no conversation to get lost in
- no chatbot
- intuitive, user knows they are submitting a post

postfinder cons
- no deniability, feels like making a public post
- custom ui/ux
- less novel than instagram chatbot
- requires signup

